人不法之利益，而竊佔他人之不動產者，依前\r\n項之規定處斷。\r\n前二項之未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/MLDM/111%2c%e8%8b%97%e7%b0%a1%2c471%2c20220520%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"MLDM,111,苗簡,471,20220520,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"苗簡","JNO":"471","JDATE":"20220520","JTITLE":"竊盜"}